#: .\m_armor.json
msgid "UN helmet"
msgid_plural "UN helmets"
msgstr[0] "聯合國頭盔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'UN helmet'}
#: .\m_armor.json
msgid ""
"A heavy helmet that provides excellent protection from all sorts of damage."
"  It is labeled as the advanced combat helmet. It is emblazoned with the "
"blue globe logo of the UN. A coveted prize amongst certain survivalist "
"types."
msgstr "一種重型頭盔，提供出色的全方位傷害防護。它被標記為高級作戰頭盔，並飾有聯合國的藍色地球標誌。是某些生存主義者夢寐以求的戰利品。"

#: .\m_armor.json
msgid "UN security vest"
msgid_plural "UN security vests"
msgstr[0] "聯合國安保背心"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'UN security vest'}
#: .\m_armor.json
msgid ""
"A bullet-resistant vest used by UN security forces deployed to the New "
"England Exlcusion zone by various obscure benefactors. Although not the best"
" ballistic protection, it is more than sufficient for most of the hazards of"
" the Exclusion Zone."
msgstr "由聯合國安全部隊使用的防彈背心，由多個不明贊助者部署到新英格蘭隔離區。雖然不是最佳的彈道防護裝備，但對於隔離區的大多數危險來說已綽綽有餘。"

#: .\m_items.json
msgid "Sailor Fuku shirt"
msgid_plural "Sailor Fuku shirts"
msgstr[0] "水手服上衣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Sailor Fuku shirt'}
#: .\m_items.json
msgid ""
"A short-sleeved cotton shirt, similar to the sailor fuku often seen in Japan"
" or anime."
msgstr "一件短袖棉質上衣，類似於日本或動漫中常見的水手服。"

#: .\m_items.json
msgid "Fuku Skirt"
msgid_plural "Fuku Skirts"
msgstr[0] "水手服短裙"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Fuku Skirt'}
#: .\m_items.json
msgid ""
"A short, breezy cotton skirt.  Easy to move in, but only has a single small "
"pocket. Commonly seen in Japan or anime."
msgstr "一條輕便的短棉裙。便於活動，但只有一個小口袋。常見於日本或動漫中。"

#: .\m_items.json
msgid "Reinforced French maid clothes"
msgid_plural "Reinforced French maid clothes"
msgstr[0] "強化法式女僕裝"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Reinforced French maid clothes', 'str_pl':
#. 'Reinforced French maid clothes'}
#: .\m_items.json
msgid ""
"The French maid dress, blue with a frilly white apron. This particular "
"version has been reinfored with Kevlar, thus turning a once near useless "
"maid dress into a genuine combat article."
msgstr "法式女僕裙，藍色配以褶邊白色圍裙。此特定版本已用凱夫拉縴維加固，從而將一件近乎無用的女僕裙轉變為真正的戰鬥裝備。"

#: .\m_items.json
msgid "Reinforced kimono"
msgid_plural "Reinforced kimonos"
msgstr[0] "強化和服"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Reinforced kimono'}
#: .\m_items.json
msgid ""
"A traditional, ankle-length Japanese robe, wrapped around the body with a "
"sash. This particular version has been reinfored with Kevlar."
msgstr "一件傳統的及踝日式長袍，用腰帶纏繞身體。此特定版本已用凱夫拉縴維加固。"

#: .\m_items.json
msgid "Reinforced yukata"
msgid_plural "Reinforced yukatas"
msgstr[0] "強化浴衣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Reinforced yukata'}
#: .\m_items.json
msgid ""
"An easy-to-wear, breezy robe secured with a sash.  Essentially Japanese "
"pajamas.  Great for summer nights. This particular version has been "
"reinfored with Kevlar."
msgstr "一件易於穿著的輕便長袍，用腰帶固定。本質上是日式睡衣，非常適合夏夜。此特定版本已用凱夫拉縴維加固。"

#: .\m_items.json
msgid "Reinforced Fuku Skirt"
msgid_plural "Reinforced Fuku Skirts"
msgstr[0] "強化水手服短裙"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Reinforced Fuku Skirt'}
#: .\m_items.json
msgid ""
"A short, breezy cotton skirt.  Easy to move in, but only has a single small "
"pocket. Commonly seen in Japan or anime. This particular version has been "
"reinfored with Kevlar."
msgstr "一條輕便的短棉裙。便於活動，但只有一個小口袋。常見於日本或動漫中。此特定版本已用凱夫拉縴維加固。"

#: .\m_items.json
msgid "Reinforced Sailor Fuku shirt"
msgid_plural "Reinforced Sailor Fuku shirts"
msgstr[0] "強化水手服上衣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Reinforced Sailor Fuku shirt'}
#: .\m_items.json
msgid ""
"A short-sleeved cotton shirt, similar to the sailor fuku often seen in Japan"
" or anime. This particular version has been reinfored with Kevlar."
msgstr "一件短袖棉襯衫，類似於日本或動漫中常見的水手服。這個特別版本用凱夫拉縴維進行了加固。"

#: .\m_items.json
msgid "pair of reinforced stockings"
msgid_plural "pairs of reinforced stockings"
msgstr[0] "一雙加固長筒襪"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of reinforced stockings', 'str_pl': 'pairs
#. of reinforced stockings'}
#: .\m_items.json
msgid ""
"Long cotton socks that reach above the knees to help protect from the cold. "
"These particular versions have been reinforced with kevlar."
msgstr "長及膝蓋以上的棉襪，有助於抵禦寒冷。這些特別版本用凱夫拉縴維進行了加固。"

#: .\m_items.json
msgid "powered exoskeleton"
msgid_plural "powered exoskeletons"
msgstr[0] "動力外骨骼"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'powered exoskeleton'}
#: .\m_items.json
msgid ""
"An articulated frame that attaches to a user's back. It allows one to lift "
"considerably more weight than one normally could, although it has a high "
"encumbrance."
msgstr "一個連接在用戶背部的鉸接框架。它允許使用者舉起比正常情況下多得多的重量，儘管它本身具有很高的負重。"

#: .\mak_rangedweaps.json
msgid "motorized crossbow"
msgid_plural "motorized crossbows"
msgstr[0] "電動弩"

#: .\mak_rangedweaps.json
msgid ""
"A modified version of the classic crossbow which utilizes stones as "
"projectiles instead of the traditional quarrel.  Uses UPS power and an "
"electric motor to activate the crossbow."
msgstr "經典弩的改良版本，使用石頭作為彈丸，而非傳統的弩箭。利用UPS電源和電動機來激活弩機。"

#: .\mak_rangedweaps.json
msgctxt "gun_type_type"
msgid "rifle"
msgstr "步槍"

#: .\mak_rangedweaps.json
msgid "large airgun"
msgid_plural "large airguns"
msgstr[0] "大型氣槍"

#: .\mak_rangedweaps.json
msgid ""
"A homemade compressed air coilgun gun, using electromagnets and compressed "
"air to accelerate a ferromagnetic projectile to high velocity.  Generally "
"too heavy to be used by a single person."
msgstr "一把自制的壓縮空氣線圈槍，利用電磁鐵和壓縮空氣將鐵磁體彈丸加速到高速。通常過於沉重，單人難以使用。"

#: .\mak_rangedweaps.json
msgid "large airgun magazine"
msgid_plural "large airgun magazines"
msgstr[0] "大型氣槍彈匣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'large airgun magazine'}
#: .\mak_rangedweaps.json
msgid ""
"An improvised magazine for use with a heavy airgun rifle.  Little more than "
"a tin can, spring and some duct tape it is awkward to reload and not "
"especially reliable."
msgstr "用於重型氣槍步槍的簡易彈匣。不過是一個錫罐、彈簧和一些膠帶，裝填笨拙且不太可靠。"

#: .\mak_rangedweaps.json
msgid "mounted heavy coilgun"
msgstr "架設式重型線圈槍"

#: .\mak_rangedweaps.json
msgid "Magnetic-Accelerated BB gun"
msgid_plural "Magnetic-Accelerated BB guns"
msgstr[0] "磁力加速BB槍"

#: .\mak_rangedweaps.json
msgid ""
"Popular among children.  It's fairly accurate, but BBs deal nearly no "
"damage. This one has been outfitted with a series of magnetic coils to "
"accelerate BBs to a high velocity."
msgstr "在兒童中很受歡迎。它相當精準，但BB彈幾乎不造成傷害。這把槍配備了一系列磁力線圈，可將BB彈加速到高速。"

#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Add Bandits Extended+"
msgstr "添加強盜擴展+"

#. ~ Description for Add Bandits Extended+
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid ""
"Modified by Malkeus, Further modified with new custom content by Jolmar7 "
"with lots of new added things. Adds bands of non-NPCs type of hostile and "
"friendly armed humans that carry weapons, ammo, that patrol the wastelands "
"looking for things to kill, each with a custom AI."
msgstr ""
"由Malkeus修改，Jolmar7進一步修改並添加了大量新的自定義內容。增加了非NPC類型的敵對和友好武裝人類團伙，他們攜帶武器彈藥，在廢土上巡邏尋找殺戮目標，每個團伙都有自定義AI。"

#: .\robot_items.json
msgid "broken bandit robot"
msgid_plural "broken bandit robots"
msgstr[0] "損壞的強盜機器人"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'broken bandit robot'}
#: .\robot_items.json
msgid ""
"A broken bandit robot, now wrecked and motionless.  It could be gutted for "
"spare parts."
msgstr "一個損壞的強盜機器人，現已報廢且靜止不動。可以拆解獲取零件。"

#: .\robot_items.json
msgid "broken maid robot"
msgid_plural "broken maid robots"
msgstr[0] "損壞的女僕機器人"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'broken maid robot'}
#: .\robot_items.json
msgid ""
"A broken maid robot, now wrecked and motionless.  It could be gutted for "
"spare parts."
msgstr "一個損壞的女僕機器人，現已報廢且靜止不動。可以拆解獲取零件。"

#: .\robot_items.json
msgid "broken school robot"
msgid_plural "broken school robots"
msgstr[0] "損壞的學校機器人"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'broken school robot'}
#: .\robot_items.json
msgid ""
"A broken school defense robot, now wrecked and motionless.  It could be "
"gutted for spare parts."
msgstr "一個損壞的學校防禦機器人，現已報廢且靜止不動。可以拆解獲取零件。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'broken school robot'}
#: .\robot_items.json
msgid ""
"A broken Industrial Mill robot, now wrecked and motionless.  It could be "
"gutted for spare parts."
msgstr "一個損壞的工業工廠機器人，現已報廢且靜止不動。可以拆解獲取零件。"

#: .\robot_items.json
msgid "broken UN Sentry Robot"
msgid_plural "broken UN Sentry Robots"
msgstr[0] "損壞的聯合國哨兵機器人"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'broken UN Sentry Robot'}
#: .\robot_items.json
msgid ""
"A broken UN Sentry Robot, now wrecked and motionless.  It could be gutted "
"for spare parts."
msgstr "一個損壞的聯合國哨兵機器人，現已報廢且靜止不動。可以拆解獲取零件。"

#: .\robot_items.json
msgid "broken security maid robot"
msgid_plural "broken security maid robots"
msgstr[0] "損壞的安保女僕機器人"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'broken security maid robot'}
#: .\robot_items.json
msgid ""
"A broken security maid robot, now wrecked and motionless.  It could be "
"gutted for spare parts."
msgstr "一個損壞的安保女僕機器人，現已報廢且靜止不動。可以拆解獲取零件。"

#: .\Monsters\closeBandits.json
msgid "Looter"
msgid_plural "Looters"
msgstr[0] "掠奪者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Looter'}
#: .\Monsters\closeBandits.json
msgid ""
"Covered in ragtag armor, the look in this one's eyes denotes desperation, a "
"common but dangerous feeling in this time."
msgstr "身披雜亂的護甲，此人眼中的神情透露出絕望，這是這個時代常見但危險的情緒。"

#: .\Monsters\closeBandits.json
msgid "Scrapper"
msgid_plural "Scrappers"
msgstr[0] "廢品客"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Scrapper'}
#: .\Monsters\closeBandits.json
msgid ""
"You can tell simply by the number of scars this survivor has that they have "
"seen many battles. Best keep your distance, because he seems all too eager "
"to get personal."
msgstr "僅憑這位倖存者身上的傷疤數量，你就能看出他經歷過許多戰鬥。最好保持距離，因為他似乎非常渴望與人近距離接觸。"

#: .\Monsters\closeBandits.json
msgid "Psycho"
msgid_plural "Psychos"
msgstr[0] "狂人"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Psycho'}
#: .\Monsters\closeBandits.json
msgid ""
"Brought to insanity through years of drug use, this crazed individual "
"brandishes a large and nasty blade and twitches anticipation for the "
"upcoming battle."
msgstr "常年吸毒導致精神失常，這個瘋狂的傢伙揮舞著一把巨大而骯髒的刀刃，因即將到來的戰鬥而興奮地抽搐。"

#: .\Monsters\closeBandits.json
msgid "Bad Doctor"
msgid_plural "Bad Doctors"
msgstr[0] "惡醫"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Bad Doctor'}
#: .\Monsters\closeBandits.json
msgid ""
"This guy's way to big to be just another bandit, and his revving chainsaw "
"only cements that fact. The one hole in his burlap-sack mask reveals a "
"bloodshot orb darting around, surveying for blood."
msgstr "這傢伙體型太大，絕非普通強盜，而他轟鳴的鏈鋸更是印證了這一點。麻袋面具上的一個孔洞露出一隻佈滿血絲的眼球，四處掃視，尋找著血腥的獵物。"

#: .\Monsters\closeBandits.json
msgid "Armored Bandit"
msgid_plural "Armored Bandits"
msgstr[0] "裝甲強盜"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Armored Bandit'}
#: .\Monsters\closeBandits.json
msgid ""
"Slightly more armored than the average bandit, this survivor stands out with"
" their break-action shotgun and satchel of shells."
msgstr "比普通強盜多了一點裝甲，這位倖存者以其折管式霰彈槍和一袋霰彈而引人注目。"

#: .\Monsters\closeBandits.json .\Monsters\closeCivilians.json
#: .\Monsters\longtroops.json
msgid "KABLAAM!!"
msgstr "轟！！"

#: .\Monsters\closeBandits.json
msgid "Raider"
msgid_plural "Raiders"
msgstr[0] "掠奪者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Raider'}
#: .\Monsters\closeBandits.json
msgid ""
"Large chunks of scrap metal drape off this bandit's duster with odd symbols "
"painted across each. They grip their shotgun sternly, almost daring some one"
" to test their mettle."
msgstr "大塊的廢金屬掛在這強盜的防塵大衣上，每塊都塗著奇怪的符號。他們緊緊握著霰彈槍，幾乎是在挑釁別人來試試他們的膽量。"

#: .\Monsters\closeBandits.json
msgid "BOOM!!"
msgstr "砰！！"

#: .\Monsters\closeBandits.json
msgid "Bandit mutt"
msgid_plural "Bandit mutts"
msgstr[0] "強盜雜種狗"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Bandit mutt'}
#: .\Monsters\closeBandits.json
msgid ""
"This once-average mixed breed dog has been trained by looters.  It's "
"probably far from harmless by now."
msgstr "這隻曾經普通的混種狗已被掠奪者訓練過。現在它很可能遠非無害。"

#: .\Monsters\closeBandits.json
msgid "Bandit Wardog"
msgid_plural "Bandit Wardogs"
msgstr[0] "強盜戰犬"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Bandit Wardog'}
#: .\Monsters\closeBandits.json
msgid ""
"This once-average mixed breed dog has been trained by looters.  This one has"
" been given rudimentary armor to protect it from damage."
msgstr "這隻曾經普通的混種狗已被掠奪者訓練過。這隻狗配備了基本的裝甲以保護其免受傷害。"

#: .\Monsters\closeBandits.json
msgid "Hacked Bandit Bot"
msgid_plural "Hacked Bandit Bots"
msgstr[0] "被黑入的強盜機器人"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Hacked Bandit Bot'}
#: .\Monsters\closeBandits.json
msgid ""
"One of the many models of armored law enforcement robots employed shortly "
"before the collapse of civilization.  Solar powered like many other robots, "
"it has been hacked by a group of bandits, propelled on a trio of omni "
"wheels."
msgstr "這是文明崩潰前不久部署的眾多裝甲執法機器人型號之一。像許多其他機器人一樣由太陽能供電，它已被一群強盜黑入，由三個全向輪驅動。"

#: .\Monsters\closeBandits.json
msgid "Angry Citizen"
msgid_plural "Angry Citizens"
msgstr[0] "憤怒市民"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Angry Citizen'}
#: .\Monsters\closeBandits.json
msgid "These people are beyond mad, and they're not gonna take it anymore!"
msgstr "這些人已經怒不可遏，他們不會再忍下去了！"

#: .\Monsters\closeBandits.json
msgid "Armed Citizen"
msgid_plural "Armed Citizens"
msgstr[0] "武裝市民"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Armed Citizen'}
#: .\Monsters\closeBandits.json
msgid ""
"These people are beyond mad, and they're not gonna take it anymore! Even "
"worse, they're now armed with .22lr pipe rifles."
msgstr "這些人已經怒不可遏，他們不會再忍下去了！更糟的是，他們現在配備了.22口徑的管狀步槍。"

#: .\Monsters\closeBandits.json
msgid "The citizen opens fire!"
msgstr "市民開火了！"

#: .\Monsters\closeBandits.json
msgid "Stalker"
msgid_plural "Stalkers"
msgstr[0] "潛行者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Stalker'}
#: .\Monsters\closeBandits.json
msgid ""
"Festooned with gear, these stalkers have entered the New England Exclusion "
"zone seeking their own treasure, or perhaps they just want the thrill of "
"adventure."
msgstr "這些潛行者裝備齊全，已進入新英格蘭隔離區尋找自己的寶藏，或者也許他們只是想要冒險的刺激。"

#: .\Monsters\closeBandits.json
msgid "Tazer Bandit"
msgid_plural "Tazer Bandits"
msgstr[0] "電擊槍強盜"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Tazer Bandit'}
#: .\Monsters\closeBandits.json
msgid ""
"This bandit is particularly unique, as they have a tazer to shock their "
"foes!"
msgstr "這個強盜尤為獨特，因為他們有一把電擊槍來電擊敵人！"

#: .\Monsters\closeBandits.json
msgid "Mounted Raider"
msgid_plural "Mounted Raiders"
msgstr[0] "騎乘掠奪者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Mounted Raider'}
#: .\Monsters\closeBandits.json
msgid ""
"This bandit is particularly unique, as they've tamed a horse to use in their"
" path of crime!"
msgstr "這個強盜尤為獨特，因為他們馴服了一匹馬用於犯罪之路！"

#: .\Monsters\closeBandits.json
msgid "Cyber Addict"
msgid_plural "Cyber Addicts"
msgstr[0] "賽博成癮者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Cyber Addict'}
#: .\Monsters\closeBandits.json
msgid ""
"You can tell simply by the number of augmentations this survivor has that "
"they've been a tech-hound for a while. Best keep your distance, this tech-"
"scav's dagger seems to glow with an electric aura."
msgstr "單從這位倖存者身上的改造數量就能看出，他們沉迷科技已有一段時間了。最好保持距離，這位科技拾荒者的匕首似乎散發著電光氣場。"

#: .\Monsters\closeBandits.json
msgid "Cyber Wanderer"
msgid_plural "Cyber Wanderers"
msgstr[0] "賽博漫遊者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Cyber Wanderer'}
#: .\Monsters\closeBandits.json
msgid ""
"A survivor of the New England Zone, this particular one has been augmented "
"by technology far beyond normal levels."
msgstr "這位新英格蘭區的倖存者，其身體已被科技改造，遠超正常水平。"

#: .\Monsters\closeBandits.json
msgid "Veteran Stalker"
msgid_plural "Veteran Stalkers"
msgstr[0] "資深潛行者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Veteran Stalker'}
#: .\Monsters\closeBandits.json
msgid ""
"Festooned with gear, these stalkers have entered the New England Exclusion "
"zone seeking their own treasure, or perhaps they just want the thrill of "
"adventure. This one is seemingly more experienced than most."
msgstr "這些潛行者裝備齊全，進入新英格蘭隔離區尋找自己的寶藏，或許他們只是渴望冒險的刺激。這一位似乎比大多數人都更有經驗。"

#: .\Monsters\closeBandits.json .\Monsters\duty_troops.json
#: .\Monsters\longBandits.json .\Monsters\longtroops.json
#: .\Monsters\midBandits.json
msgid "CRACK!!"
msgstr "咔嚓！！"

#: .\Monsters\closeCivilians.json
msgid "Civilian Farmer"
msgid_plural "Civilian Farmers"
msgstr[0] "平民農夫"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Civilian Farmer'}
#: .\Monsters\closeCivilians.json
msgid ""
"A farmer too stubborn to leave New England once the Federal Government "
"enforced the Exclusion Zone."
msgstr "一位固執的農夫，在聯邦政府強制執行隔離區後拒絕離開新英格蘭。"

#: .\Monsters\closeCivilians.json
msgid "Melee Scavenger"
msgid_plural "Melee Scavengers"
msgstr[0] "近戰拾荒者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Melee Scavenger'}
#: .\Monsters\closeCivilians.json
msgid ""
"Whether he's driven by greed for the riches left behind in the exclusion "
"zone or simply refused to leave doesn't matter. What does matter is that "
"this scav will probably try to kill you."
msgstr "無論他是被隔離區遺留財富的貪婪驅使，還是單純拒絕離開，都不重要。重要的是這個拾荒者很可能會試圖殺了你。"

#: .\Monsters\closeCivilians.json .\New NPCs\mak_redneck.json
msgid "Redneck"
msgid_plural "Rednecks"
msgstr[0] "紅脖子"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Redneck'}
#: .\Monsters\closeCivilians.json
msgid ""
"Trusting their firearms more than the government, these hardy rednecks "
"refused to leave the New England exlusion zone. They might be friendly, or "
"they might not."
msgstr "這些頑強的紅脖子更信任自己的槍械而非政府，拒絕離開新英格蘭隔離區。他們可能友善，也可能不。"

#: .\Monsters\closeCivilians.json
msgid "shelter survivor"
msgid_plural "shelter survivors"
msgstr[0] "避難所幸存者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'shelter survivor'}
#: .\Monsters\closeCivilians.json
msgid ""
"A survivor too stubborn to leave New England once the Federal Government "
"enforced the Exclusion Zone. They now live in an LMOE shelter"
msgstr "一位固執的倖存者，在聯邦政府強制執行隔離區後拒絕離開新英格蘭。他們現在居住在一個LMOE避難所中。"

#: .\Monsters\closeCivilians.json
msgid "shelter guard"
msgid_plural "shelter guards"
msgstr[0] "避難所守衛"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'shelter guard'}
#: .\Monsters\closeCivilians.json
msgid ""
"A survivor too stubborn to leave New England once the Federal Government "
"enforced the Exclusion Zone. They now live in an LMOE shelter. Be careful, "
"this one is armed!"
msgstr "一位固執的倖存者，在聯邦政府強制執行隔離區後拒絕離開新英格蘭。他們現在居住在一個LMOE避難所中。小心，這一位是武裝的！"

#: .\Monsters\closeCivilians.json
msgid "noise explodes from the survivor's gun!"
msgstr "倖存者的槍爆發出巨響！"

#: .\Monsters\closeCultist.json
msgid "Cultist Acolyte"
msgid_plural "Cultist Acolytes"
msgstr[0] "邪教徒侍僧"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Cultist Acolyte'}
#: .\Monsters\closeCultist.json
msgid ""
"Covered in ragtag armor, the look in this one's eyes denotes devotion, a "
"rare but dangerous feeling in the exclusion zone."
msgstr "身披破舊盔甲，此人眼中的神情透露出虔誠，這在隔離區是一種罕見但危險的情感。"

#: .\Monsters\closeCultist.json
msgid "Armored Cultist"
msgid_plural "Armored Cultists"
msgstr[0] "裝甲邪教徒"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Armored Cultist'}
#: .\Monsters\closeCultist.json
msgid ""
"Covered in scrapped-together armor, the look in this one's eyes denotes "
"devotion, a rare but dangerous feeling in the exclusion zone."
msgstr "身披拼湊而成的盔甲，此人眼中的神情透露出虔誠，這在隔離區是一種罕見但危險的情感。"

#: .\Monsters\closeCultist.json
msgid "Anointed Cultist"
msgid_plural "Anointed Cultists"
msgstr[0] "受膏邪教徒"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Anointed Cultist'}
#: .\Monsters\closeCultist.json
msgid ""
"Covered in a purpose built robe of war, the look in this one's eyes denotes "
"devotion, a rare but dangerous feeling in the exclusion zone."
msgstr "身披特製的戰爭長袍，此人眼中的神情透露出虔誠，這在隔離區是一種罕見但危險的情感。"

#: .\Monsters\closeCultist.json
msgid "UN Riot Guard"
msgid_plural "UN Riot Guards"
msgstr[0] "聯合國防暴衛兵"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'UN Riot Guard'}
#: .\Monsters\closeCultist.json
msgid ""
"Initially deployed at the behest of nebulous foreign benefactors, the UN "
"Riot Guard has become a stable of the New England Exclusion zone. Often well"
" trained, these foreign soldiers will shoot first and never ask questions."
msgstr "最初應模糊不清的外國資助者要求部署，聯合國防暴衛兵已成為新英格蘭隔離區的穩定存在。這些外國士兵通常訓練有素，會先開槍且從不提問。"

#: .\Monsters\closePrisoner.json
msgid "Prisoner"
msgid_plural "Prisoners"
msgstr[0] "囚犯"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Prisoner'}
#: .\Monsters\closePrisoner.json
msgid ""
"Left behind by the government to fend for himself, this former prisoner has "
"been give a new lease on life. But perhaps he wants to take your life as "
"well."
msgstr "被政府遺棄自生自滅，這位前囚犯獲得了新生。但或許他也想奪走你的生命。"

#: .\Monsters\closePrisoner.json
msgid "Armored Prisoner"
msgid_plural "Armored Prisoners"
msgstr[0] "裝甲囚犯"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Armored Prisoner'}
#: .\Monsters\closePrisoner.json
msgid ""
"Covered in scrapped-together armor, Left behind by the government to fend "
"for himself, this former prisoner has been give a new lease on life. But "
"perhaps he wants to take your life as well."
msgstr "身披拼湊而成的盔甲，被政府遺棄自生自滅，這位前囚犯獲得了新生。但或許他也想奪走你的生命。"

#: .\Monsters\closeToxic.json
msgid "Hazardous Melee Prospector"
msgid_plural "Hazardous Melee Prospectors"
msgstr[0] "危險近戰勘探者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Hazardous Melee Prospector'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Hazardous Gun Prospector'}
#: .\Monsters\closeToxic.json
msgid ""
"Covered in chemically protective armor, this prospector has begun to look "
"for loot in hazardous areas out of desperation."
msgstr "身披化學防護裝甲，這位勘探者出於絕望，開始在危險區域尋找戰利品。"

#: .\Monsters\closeToxic.json
msgid "Hazardous Gun Prospector"
msgid_plural "Hazardous Gun Prospectors"
msgstr[0] "危險槍械勘探者"

#: .\Monsters\closeToxic.json
msgid "The prospector opens fire!"
msgstr "勘探者開火了！"

#: .\Monsters\closeToxic.json
msgid "Mutant Melee Prospector"
msgid_plural "Mutant Melee Prospectors"
msgstr[0] "變異近戰勘探者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Mutant Melee Prospector'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Mutant Gun Prospector'}
#: .\Monsters\closeToxic.json
msgid ""
"Covered in chemically protective armor, this prospector has begun to look "
"for loot in hazardous areas out of desperation. The suit has become cracked "
"and punctured, revealing the taint of mutation beneath."
msgstr "身著化學防護裝甲，這名勘探者出於絕望開始在危險區域搜尋戰利品。護甲已出現裂痕與破洞，暴露出底下突變的汙染痕跡。"

#: .\Monsters\closeToxic.json
msgid "Mutant Gun Prospector"
msgid_plural "Mutant Gun Prospectors"
msgstr[0] "突變槍手勘探者"

#: .\Monsters\closeToxic.json
msgid "noise explodes from the prospector's gun!"
msgstr "勘探者的槍爆發出巨響！"

#: .\Monsters\closeToxic.json
msgid "Acid Prospector"
msgid_plural "Acid Prospectors"
msgstr[0] "酸液勘探者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Acid Prospector'}
#: .\Monsters\closeToxic.json
msgid ""
"Covered in chemically protective armor, this prospector has begun to look "
"for loot in hazardous areas out of desperation. Watch out, this one has a "
"chemical-sprayer!"
msgstr "身著化學防護裝甲，這名勘探者出於絕望開始在危險區域搜尋戰利品。小心，這傢伙配備了化學噴射器！"

#: .\Monsters\closecivrobots.json
msgid "Maid Robot"
msgid_plural "Maid Robots"
msgstr[0] "女僕機器人"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Maid Robot'}
#: .\Monsters\closecivrobots.json
msgid ""
"One of the few models of personal maid robot produced before the creation of"
" the exclusion zone.  Produced by Chi industries, these maid robots have "
"become items with their own extensive aftermarket consumer base."
msgstr "這是在隔離區建立前生產的少數個人女僕機器人型號之一。由Chi工業製造，這些女僕機器人已成為擁有龐大二手消費市場的物品。"

#: .\Monsters\closecivrobots.json
msgid "School Defense Robot"
msgid_plural "School Defense Robots"
msgstr[0] "學校防衛機器人"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'School Defense Robot'}
#: .\Monsters\closecivrobots.json
msgid ""
"A recent design made in order to defend schools from a variety of "
"assailants, both inside and out. Even though New England Schools are no "
"longer in session, these robots still patrol the hallways as metal vigils."
msgstr "這是為防禦學校內外各類襲擊者而設計的近期型號。儘管新英格蘭的學校已不再上課，這些機器人仍如金屬哨兵般在走廊中巡邏。"

#: .\Monsters\closecivrobots.json
msgid "Industrial Mill Robot"
msgid_plural "Industrial Mill Robots"
msgstr[0] "工業工廠機器人"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Industrial Mill Robot'}
#: .\Monsters\closecivrobots.json
msgid ""
"An older design made in order to work at dangerous locations such as "
"factories and steel mills. Even though New England factories are no longer "
"producing anything other than rust, these robots still do their work."
msgstr "這是為在工廠和鋼鐵廠等危險場所工作而設計的舊型號。儘管新英格蘭的工廠除了鏽蝕已不再生產任何東西，這些機器人仍在執行它們的任務。"

#: .\Monsters\closecivrobots.json
msgid "UN Perimeter Defense Robot"
msgid_plural "UN Perimeter Defense Robots"
msgstr[0] "聯合國外圍防衛機器人"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'UN Perimeter Defense Robot'}
#: .\Monsters\closecivrobots.json
msgid ""
"Covered in a distinctive blue coat of paint, these dangerous droids patrol "
"around UN encampments for potential scavs or mercenaries. They don't "
"discriminate against any non-UN targets."
msgstr "塗有獨特的藍色塗層，這些危險的機器人在聯合國營地周圍巡邏，防範潛在的拾荒者或僱傭兵。它們對任何非聯合國目標都一視同仁地攻擊。"

#: .\Monsters\closecivrobots.json .\Monsters\duty_troops.json
#: .\Monsters\longBandits.json .\Monsters\longtroops.json
msgid "P-P-P-POW"
msgstr "砰-砰-砰-砰"

#: .\Monsters\closecivrobots.json
msgid "Robot Maid Security"
msgid_plural "Robot Maid Securitys"
msgstr[0] "機器人女僕保安"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Robot Maid Security'}
#: .\Monsters\closecivrobots.json
msgid ""
"One of the few models of personal maid security robot produced before the "
"creation of the exclusion zone.  Produced by Chi industries, these security "
"robots have become items with their own extensive aftermarket consumer base."
msgstr "這是在隔離區建立前生產的少數個人女僕保安機器人型號之一。由Chi工業製造，這些保安機器人已成為擁有龐大二手消費市場的物品。"

#: .\Monsters\duty_troops.json
msgid "Duty recruit"
msgid_plural "Duty recruits"
msgstr[0] "義務團新兵"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Duty recruit'}
#: .\Monsters\duty_troops.json
msgid ""
"A recruit whose interest in the zone led them to joining Duty, a faction "
"whose primary interest is maintaning some semblance of order within the New "
"England Exclusion Zone."
msgstr "一名因對區域感興趣而加入義務團的新兵，該派系的主要目標是在新英格蘭隔離區內維持某種秩序的表象。"

#: .\Monsters\duty_troops.json
msgid "The recruit's pistol explodes in light and sound!"
msgstr "新兵的手槍爆發出光與聲！"

#: .\Monsters\duty_troops.json
msgid "Duty officer"
msgid_plural "Duty officers"
msgstr[0] "義務團軍官"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Duty officer'}
#: .\Monsters\duty_troops.json
msgid ""
"An officer whose interest in the zone led them to joining Duty, a faction "
"whose primary interest is maintaning some semblance of order within the New "
"England Exclusion Zone."
msgstr "一名因對區域感興趣而加入義務團的軍官，該派系的主要目標是在新英格蘭隔離區內維持某種秩序的表象。"

#: .\Monsters\duty_troops.json
msgid "The officer's pistol explodes in light and sound!"
msgstr "軍官的手槍爆發出光與聲！"

#: .\Monsters\duty_troops.json
msgid "Duty soldier"
msgid_plural "Duty soldiers"
msgstr[0] "義務團士兵"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Duty soldier'}
#: .\Monsters\duty_troops.json
msgid ""
"A soldier whose interest in the zone led them to joining Duty, a faction "
"whose primary interest is maintaning some semblance of order within the New "
"England Exclusion Zone."
msgstr "一名因對區域感興趣而加入義務團的士兵，該派系的主要目標是在新英格蘭隔離區內維持某種秩序的表象。"

#: .\Monsters\duty_troops.json
msgid "armored Duty trooper"
msgid_plural "armored Duty troopers"
msgstr[0] "裝甲義務團士兵"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'armored Duty trooper'}
#: .\Monsters\duty_troops.json
msgid ""
"A soldier whose interest in the zone led them to joining Duty, a faction "
"whose primary interest is maintaning some semblance of order within the New "
"England Exclusion Zone. This one has eschewed firearms in lieu of a riot "
"shield and a baton, watch out!"
msgstr "一名因對區域感興趣而加入義務團的士兵，該派系的主要目標是在新英格蘭隔離區內維持某種秩序的表象。此人放棄了槍械，改用防暴盾和警棍，小心！"

#: .\Monsters\duty_troops.json
msgid "Duty exoskeleton soldier"
msgid_plural "Duty exoskeleton soldiers"
msgstr[0] "義務團外骨骼士兵"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Duty exoskeleton soldier'}
#: .\Monsters\duty_troops.json
msgid ""
"A soldier whose interest in the zone led them to joining Duty, a faction "
"whose primary interest is maintaning some semblance of order within the New "
"England Exclusion Zone. This one wears a powerful exoskeleton!"
msgstr "一名因對區域感興趣而加入義務團的士兵，該派系的主要目標是在新英格蘭隔離區內維持某種秩序的表象。此人穿著強大的外骨骼！"

#: .\Monsters\fbi_unit.json
msgid "FBI X-Operative"
msgid_plural "FBI X-Operatives"
msgstr[0] "聯邦調查局X特工"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'FBI X-Operative'}
#: .\Monsters\fbi_unit.json
msgid ""
"Although the US government has largely left the New England SEZ, some FBI "
"units have been inserted to observe from time to time. It's not entirely "
"known as to what their purpose is, but the strange lovecraftian creatures "
"might give a clue."
msgstr ""
"儘管美國政府已基本撤出新英格蘭特別經濟區，但一些聯邦調查局小隊仍不時被派遣進行觀察。他們的目的尚不完全明確，但那些詭異的洛夫克拉夫特式生物或許能提供線索。"

#: .\Monsters\lab_securitymon.json
msgid "Melee Security Guard"
msgid_plural "Melee Security Guards"
msgstr[0] "近戰安保警衛"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Melee Security Guard'}
#: .\Monsters\lab_securitymon.json
msgid ""
"One of the few guards left behind in the laboratories of New England after "
"evacuation. Their purpose is unknown, but they're more than willing to kill "
"people who get in their way. This one has a security baton."
msgstr "撤離後，新英格蘭實驗室中少數留守的警衛之一。他們的目的不明，但非常樂意清除擋路者。此人配備安保警棍。"

#: .\Monsters\lab_securitymon.json
msgid "Security Guard"
msgid_plural "Security Guards"
msgstr[0] "安保警衛"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Security Guard'}
#: .\Monsters\lab_securitymon.json
msgid ""
"One of the few guards left behind in the laboratories of New England after "
"evacuation. Their purpose is unknown, but they're more than willing to kill "
"people who get in their way. This one has a pistol."
msgstr "撤離後，新英格蘭實驗室中少數留守的警衛之一。他們的目的不明，但非常樂意清除擋路者。此人配備手槍。"

#: .\Monsters\lab_securitymon.json
msgid "The guard opens fire!"
msgstr "警衛開火了！"

#: .\Monsters\lab_securitymon.json
msgid "Scientist"
msgid_plural "Scientists"
msgstr[0] "科學家"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Scientist'}
#: .\Monsters\lab_securitymon.json
msgid ""
"A scientist tasked with researching a wide variety of trends in the zone, "
"both natural and unnatural."
msgstr "一位負責研究區域內各種自然與非自然現象的科學家。"

#: .\Monsters\lab_securitymon.json
msgid "Hazmat Science Security"
msgid_plural "Hazmat Science Securitys"
msgstr[0] "防化科學安保"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Hazmat Science Security'}
#: .\Monsters\lab_securitymon.json
msgid ""
"One of the few guards left behind in the laboratories of New England after "
"evacuation. Their purpose is unknown, but they're more than willing to kill "
"people who get in their way. This one has a submachine gun and acid-proof "
"hazmat suit."
msgstr "撤離後，新英格蘭實驗室中少數留守的警衛之一。他們的目的不明，但非常樂意清除擋路者。此人配備衝鋒槍和防酸防護服。"

#: .\Monsters\lab_securitymon.json
msgid "noise explodes from the guard's gun!"
msgstr "警衛的槍爆發出巨響！"

#: .\Monsters\longBandits.json
msgid "Marksman"
msgid_plural "Marksmans"
msgstr[0] "神射手"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Marksman'}
#: .\Monsters\longBandits.json
msgid ""
"Clothed in a battered duster, this survivor grips his rifle with predatory "
"intentions."
msgstr "身披破舊風衣，這位倖存者緊握步槍，帶著捕食者的意圖。"

#: .\Monsters\longBandits.json
msgid "Head Hunter"
msgid_plural "Head Hunters"
msgstr[0] "獵頭者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Head Hunter'}
#: .\Monsters\longBandits.json
msgid ""
"It's incredibly difficult to see this guillied-up survivor amoungst their "
"surroundings. A few seconds later and it might have been too late to notice "
"him. Maybe it already is."
msgstr "極難在環境中發現這位披著偽裝服的倖存者。再晚幾秒，可能就來不及注意到他了。或許已經太遲了。"

#: .\Monsters\longBandits.json
msgid "Marauder"
msgid_plural "Marauders"
msgstr[0] "掠奪者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Marauder'}
#: .\Monsters\longBandits.json
msgid ""
"Covered in head to toe in piecemeal armor, it's hard to tell that there is "
"no mere human behind that gasmask. Clued-in by his unnatural grace and "
"beastial posture, it is safe to assume this bandit has modified himself well"
" beyond human limits."
msgstr "從頭到腳覆蓋著拼湊的護甲，很難分辨防毒面具後是否僅為凡人。從其非自然的優雅與野獸般的姿態推斷，可以確定這名匪徒已將自己改造得遠超人類極限。"

#: .\Monsters\longBandits.json
msgid "Black Powder Remnant"
msgid_plural "Black Powder Remnants"
msgstr[0] "黑火藥殘餘者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Black Powder Remnant'}
#: .\Monsters\longBandits.json
msgid ""
"Clothed in a rustic gear, this remnant refused to leave the zone. They've "
"resorted to defending themselves with black-powder weapons."
msgstr "身著粗陋裝備，這位殘餘者拒絕離開區域。他們轉而使用黑火藥武器自衛。"

#: .\Monsters\longtroops.json
msgid "UN Peacekeeper"
msgid_plural "UN Peacekeepers"
msgstr[0] "聯合國維和人員"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'UN Peacekeeper'}
#: .\Monsters\longtroops.json
msgid ""
"Initially deployed at the behest of nebulous foreign benefactors, the UN "
"Peacekeeper has become a staple of the New England Exclusion zone. Often "
"well trained, these foreign soldiers will shoot first and never ask "
"questions."
msgstr "最初受模糊的外國資助者委派部署，聯合國維和人員已成為新英格蘭隔離區的常客。這些外國士兵通常訓練有素，會先開槍且從不提問。"

#: .\Monsters\longtroops.json
msgid "USEC Security Merc"
msgid_plural "USEC Security Mercs"
msgstr[0] "USEC安保傭兵"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'USEC Security Merc'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'USEC Shotgun Merc'}
#: .\Monsters\longtroops.json
msgid ""
"Initially deployed at the behest of nebulous foreign benefactors, the USEC "
"has become a staple of the New England Exclusion zone. Often seen fighting "
"scavs, Bear mercenaries and UN Peacekeepers."
msgstr "最初受模糊的外國資助者委派部署，USEC已成為新英格蘭隔離區的常客。常見他們與拾荒者、熊傭兵和聯合國維和人員交戰。"

#: .\Monsters\longtroops.json
msgid "USEC Shotgun Merc"
msgid_plural "USEC Shotgun Mercs"
msgstr[0] "USEC霰彈槍傭兵"

#: .\Monsters\longtroops.json
msgid "Ranged Scavenger"
msgid_plural "Ranged Scavengers"
msgstr[0] "遠程拾荒者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Ranged Scavenger'}
#: .\Monsters\longtroops.json
msgid ""
"Whether she's driven by greed for the riches left behind in the exclusion "
"zone or simply refused to leave doesn't matter. What does matter is that "
"this scav will probably try to kill you"
msgstr "無論她是被隔離區遺留的財富所驅使，還是單純拒絕離開，都不重要。重要的是，這名拾荒者很可能會試圖殺死你。"

#: .\Monsters\longtroops.json
msgid "Bow Bandit"
msgid_plural "Bow Bandits"
msgstr[0] "弓箭匪徒"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Bow Bandit'}
#: .\Monsters\longtroops.json
msgid ""
"Perhaps they were mocked for taking an interest in archery at some point, "
"well people aren't laughing anymore"
msgstr "或許他們曾因對射箭感興趣而遭嘲笑，但現在沒人再笑了。"

#: .\Monsters\longtroops.json
msgid "Bow Wanderer"
msgid_plural "Bow Wanderers"
msgstr[0] "弓箭漫遊者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Bow Wanderer'}
#: .\Monsters\longtroops.json
msgid ""
"Honed by the carnage of New England, these particular bandits have honed the"
" art of archery into a vicious art of war."
msgstr "在新英格蘭的殺戮中磨礪，這些特殊的匪徒已將射箭技藝精煉成一種兇殘的戰爭藝術。"

#: .\Monsters\longtroops.json
msgid "Mallninja Lite"
msgid_plural "Mallninja Lites"
msgstr[0] "輕量級商場忍者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Mallninja Lite'}
#: .\Monsters\longtroops.json
msgid ""
"A denizen of the shopping mall, this person has defined themselves by a "
"nearly obsessive interest in firearms. These kinds of people have been "
"mocked for years, but perhaps now they will see their time in the sun."
msgstr "這位購物中心的居民，以近乎痴迷的槍械興趣定義了自己。這類人多年來一直備受嘲笑，但或許現在他們將迎來自己的輝煌時刻。"

#: .\Monsters\longtroops.json
msgid "The mallninja opens fire!"
msgstr "商場忍者開火了！"

#: .\Monsters\longtroops.json
msgid "Mallninja Pro"
msgid_plural "Mallninja Pros"
msgstr[0] "商場忍者專家"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Mallninja Pro'}
#: .\Monsters\longtroops.json
msgid ""
"A denizen of the shopping mall, this person has defined themselves by a "
"nearly obsessive interest in firearms. These kinds of people have been "
"mocked for years, but perhaps now they will see their time in the sun. This "
"one has become rather skilled, not just in theory but in practice as well."
msgstr ""
"這位購物中心的居民，以近乎痴迷的槍械興趣定義了自己。這類人多年來一直備受嘲笑，但或許現在他們將迎來自己的輝煌時刻。這一位已經相當熟練，不僅在理論上，在實踐中也是如此。"

#: .\Monsters\longtroops.json
msgid "Bandit Gunner"
msgid_plural "Bandit Gunners"
msgstr[0] "強盜槍手"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Bandit Gunner'}
#: .\Monsters\longtroops.json
msgid ""
"Equipped with a rifle, this bandit can shoot people from a much longer range"
" than most!."
msgstr "裝備著步槍，這名強盜能從比大多數人遠得多的距離射擊！"

#: .\Monsters\longtroops.json
msgid "Levergun Outlaw"
msgid_plural "Levergun Outlaws"
msgstr[0] "槓桿槍法外之徒"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Levergun Outlaw'}
#: .\Monsters\longtroops.json
msgid ""
"Equipped with a lever-action gun of the old west, this bandit thinks this "
"town isn't big enough for the both of you."
msgstr "裝備著舊西部的槓桿式步槍，這名強盜認為這個鎮子容不下你們倆。"

#: .\Monsters\midBandits.json
msgid "Bandit"
msgid_plural "Bandits"
msgstr[0] "強盜"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Bandit'}
#: .\Monsters\midBandits.json
msgid ""
"A look of cold malice can be found in this survivor's eye. Seeing you "
"approach, they ready their pistol."
msgstr "這名倖存者眼中透出冰冷的惡意。看到你靠近，他們舉起了手槍。"

#: .\Monsters\midBandits.json
msgid "The bandit opens fire!"
msgstr "強盜開火了！"

#: .\Monsters\midBandits.json
msgid "Highwayman"
msgid_plural "Highwaymans"
msgstr[0] "攔路強盜"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Highwayman'}
#: .\Monsters\midBandits.json
msgid ""
"This particular survivor seems a tad more well-off than his companions. "
"Brandishing a well-kept pistol, his eyes dart around eagerly, looking for "
"another source of good loot."
msgstr "這名倖存者似乎比他的同伴們稍微富裕一些。揮舞著一把保養良好的手槍，他的眼睛急切地掃視四周，尋找另一個好戰利品的來源。"

#: .\Monsters\midBandits.json
msgid "The highwayman's pistol explodes in light and sound!"
msgstr "攔路強盜的手槍爆發出火光與聲響！"

#: .\Monsters\midBandits.json
msgid "Outlaw"
msgid_plural "Outlaws"
msgstr[0] "法外之徒"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Outlaw'}
#: .\Monsters\midBandits.json
msgid ""
"A crazed gunman out for blood, he doesn't hesitate to brandish his "
"submachinegun at the mere hint of potential prey."
msgstr "一名嗜血的瘋狂槍手，他毫不猶豫地揮舞著衝鋒槍，僅僅因為一絲潛在獵物的跡象。"

#: .\Monsters\midBandits.json
msgid "noise explodes from the outlaw's gun!"
msgstr "法外之徒的槍爆發出噪音！"

#: .\Monsters\midBandits.json
msgid "Mounted Pistoleer"
msgid_plural "Mounted Pistoleers"
msgstr[0] "騎手槍手"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Mounted Pistoleer'}
#: .\Monsters\midBandits.json
msgid ""
"This bandit is particularly unique, with their six-shooter and trusty horse,"
" their path of crime is without end!"
msgstr "這名強盜尤為獨特，手持六發左輪手槍，騎著可靠的馬匹，他的犯罪之路永無止境！"

#: .\Monsters\midBandits.json
msgid "The pistoleer opens fire!"
msgstr "騎手槍手開火了！"

#: .\Monsters\midBandits.json
msgid "bandit walker"
msgid_plural "bandit walkers"
msgstr[0] "強盜步行者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'bandit walker'}
#: .\Monsters\midBandits.json
msgid ""
"The Northrop ATSV, a massive, heavily-armed and armored robot walking on a "
"pair of reverse-jointed legs. Somehow, bandits managed to hack into a broken"
" one and turned a pile of scrap into a weapon of war. One of its combat arms"
" has been destroyed, leaving it only with a machine gun for combat."
msgstr ""
"諾斯羅普 "
"ATSV，一個巨大的、全副武裝且裝甲的機器人，靠一對反關節腿行走。不知何故，強盜們設法黑進了一個損壞的機器人，將一堆廢鐵變成了戰爭武器。它的一條戰鬥臂已被摧毀，只剩下機槍用於戰鬥。"

