msgstr "謝謝你的信息。"

#: .\New NPCs\mak_UN_troop.json
msgid "UN Trooper"
msgstr "聯合國特遣隊員"

#: .\New NPCs\mak_UN_troop.json
msgid "Is a soldier representing the United Nations Security Detail."
msgstr "是代表聯合國安保部隊的士兵。"

#: .\New NPCs\mak_UN_troop.json
msgid "How are you even speaking to me?"
msgstr "你到底是怎麼跟我說話的？"

#: .\New NPCs\mak_UN_troop.json
msgid "So you're a soldier for the UN, what's that like?"
msgstr "所以你是為聯合國效力的士兵，感覺怎麼樣？"

#: .\New NPCs\mak_UN_troop.json
msgid "Pretty fun, but again, how are you even speaking to me?"
msgstr "挺有意思的，但再說一遍，你到底是怎麼跟我說話的？"

#: .\New NPCs\mak_UN_troop.json
msgid "UN Sniper"
msgstr "聯合國狙擊手"

#: .\New NPCs\mak_USEC_troop.json
msgid "USEC Trooper"
msgstr "USEC 特遣隊員"

#: .\New NPCs\mak_factions.json
msgid "Rednecks"
msgstr "紅脖子"

#. ~ Description for Rednecks
#: .\New NPCs\mak_factions.json
msgid ""
"A loose coalition of trailer park denizens and backcountry citizens who "
"decided not to leave New England when the going got good. Generally "
"friendly, although wary of outsiders."
msgstr "一個由拖車公園居民和偏遠地區公民組成的鬆散聯盟，他們在局勢好轉時決定不離開新英格蘭。通常友好，但對陌生人保持警惕。"

#: .\New NPCs\mak_factions.json
msgid "United Nations Security Forces"
msgstr "聯合國安保部隊"

#. ~ Description for United Nations Security Forces
#: .\New NPCs\mak_factions.json
msgid ""
"Representatives of the United Nations who were sent to the New England "
"Exclusion zone as 'peacekeepers' by institutional forces difficult to "
"identify. Despite their moniker as peacekeepers, they are often very violent"
" towards anybody that comes across their field of view, killing them on the "
"spot."
msgstr ""
"聯合國的代表，被難以識別的體制力量作為“維和人員”派往新英格蘭隔離區。儘管被稱為維和人員，他們卻常常對進入視野的任何人採取極端暴力，當場格殺。"

#: .\New NPCs\mak_factions.json
msgid "Hostile Survivors"
msgstr "敵對倖存者"

#. ~ Description for Hostile Survivors
#: .\New NPCs\mak_factions.json
msgid ""
"A very, very loose collection of bandits, stragglers, stay-behinds and "
"malcontents that decided to stay in the New England Exclusion Zone after the"
" collapse of New England."
msgstr "一個極其鬆散的集合體，包括土匪、散兵遊勇、留守者和不滿分子，他們在新英格蘭崩潰後決定留在新英格蘭隔離區。"

#: .\New NPCs\mak_factions.json
msgid "Friendly Survivors"
msgstr "友好倖存者"

#. ~ Description for Friendly Survivors
#: .\New NPCs\mak_factions.json
msgid ""
"A very, very loose collection of civilians, stragglers, stay-behinds and "
"wanderers that decided to stay in the New England Exclusion Zone after the "
"collapse of New England."
msgstr "一個極其鬆散的集合體，包括平民、散兵遊勇、留守者和流浪者，他們在新英格蘭崩潰後決定留在新英格蘭隔離區。"

#: .\New NPCs\mak_factions.json
msgid "Farmers"
msgstr "農民"

#. ~ Description for Farmers
#: .\New NPCs\mak_factions.json
msgid ""
"Farmers, Ranchhands and animal husbandry experts that decided to live off "
"the grid on their farms rather than leave New England."
msgstr "農民、牧場工人和畜牧專家，他們決定在自己的農場裡離網生活，而不是離開新英格蘭。"

#: .\New NPCs\mak_factions.json
msgid "USEC"
msgstr "USEC"

#. ~ Description for USEC
#: .\New NPCs\mak_factions.json
msgid ""
"USEC, or United Security, is a private military contractor that has been "
"deployed to the New England Exclusion zone to defend or secure the financial"
" interests of unknown parties. Their primary enemies are the similarly "
"famous BEAR mercenaries."
msgstr ""
"USEC，即聯合安保，是一傢俬營軍事承包商，被部署到新英格蘭隔離區，以捍衛或確保未知方的經濟利益。他們的主要敵人是同樣著名的BEAR僱傭兵。"

#: .\New NPCs\mak_factions.json
msgid "BEAR"
msgstr "BEAR"

#. ~ Description for BEAR
#: .\New NPCs\mak_factions.json
msgid ""
"BEAR, or Battle Encounter Assault Regiment, is a private military contractor"
" that has been deployed to the New England Exclusion zone to defend or "
"secure the financial interests of unknown parties. Their primary enemies are"
" the similarly famous USEC mercenaries. Primarily recruited from Russia and "
"various post-soviet states."
msgstr ""
"BEAR，即戰鬥遭遇突擊團，是一傢俬營軍事承包商，被部署到新英格蘭隔離區，以捍衛或確保未知方的經濟利益。他們的主要敵人是同樣著名的USEC僱傭兵。主要從俄羅斯及各個後蘇聯國家招募。"

#: .\New NPCs\mak_factions.json
msgid "Militia Group"
msgstr "民兵組織"

#. ~ Description for Militia Group
#: .\New NPCs\mak_factions.json
msgid ""
"One of the militia groups is a loose confederation of various political "
"groups, survialists and armed factions that managed to survive the tumult of"
" the early cataclsym. Already cloistered and paranoid before the war, this "
"group of people found themselves acclimating to their new environment better"
" than most."
msgstr ""
"其中一個民兵組織是各種政治團體、生存主義者和武裝派系的鬆散聯盟，他們在早期災難的動盪中倖存下來。戰前就已封閉且偏執，這群人發現自己比大多數人更能適應新環境。"

#: .\New NPCs\mak_farmer.json
msgid "farmer"
msgstr "農夫"

#: .\New NPCs\mak_farmer.json NPCs\mak_redneck.json
msgid "A backwoods denizen that decided not to leave New England."
msgstr "一個決定不離開新英格蘭的偏遠居民。"

#: .\New NPCs\mak_farmer.json
msgid "It's almost harvesting season."
msgstr "收穫季節快到了。"

#: .\New NPCs\mak_farmer.json
msgid "Less talking, more farming!."
msgstr "少說話，多幹活！"

#: .\New NPCs\mak_farmer.json
msgid "I'm so thankful for having this farm, at least we won't starve."
msgstr "我很慶幸擁有這個農場，至少我們不會捱餓。"

#: .\New NPCs\mak_farmer.json
msgid ""
"It's almost peaceful out here, you know? Well, besides the horrible things "
"that roam the forests and have made the cities and towns their stomping "
"grounds.."
msgstr "這裡幾乎很平靜，你知道嗎？嗯，除了那些在森林裡遊蕩、把城鎮當作據點的可怕東西。"

#: .\New NPCs\mak_farmer.json
msgid "What brings a lady like you to our little farm?"
msgstr "是什麼風把你這樣的女士吹到我們的小農場來的？"

#: .\New NPCs\mak_farmer.json
msgid "What brings a man like you to our little farm?"
msgstr "是什麼風把你這樣的男士吹到我們的小農場來的？"

#: .\New NPCs\mak_farmer.json
msgid "So you decided to stay on your farm, why is that?."
msgstr "所以你決定留在你的農場，這是為什麼？"

#: .\New NPCs\mak_farmer.json NPCs\Militia NPCs\amg_gun_merchant.json
msgid "Would you be willing to let me buy anything?"
msgstr "你願意讓我買點東西嗎？"

#: .\New NPCs\mak_farmer.json
msgid ""
"What, leave my farm, probably the only place I've ever really known, to go "
"off to goodness knows where with those evac shelters? Sure, it's more "
"dangerous now than before, but I just can't bring myself to leave the "
"exclusion zone. Besides, we're not really bothered much anyway, the dangers "
"around seemingly have no desire to move that far, it's rather strange if you"
" think about it."
msgstr ""
"什麼，離開我的農場——可能是我唯一真正熟悉的地方——跟著那些疏散收容所去天知道的地方？當然，現在比以前更危險了，但我就是沒法讓自己離開隔離區。再說了，我們其實也沒怎麼被打擾，周圍的危險似乎沒有意願走那麼遠，仔細想想還挺奇怪的。"

#: .\New NPCs\mak_redneck.json
msgid "Seen any varmints around lately?."
msgstr "最近看到什麼害獸了嗎？"

#: .\New NPCs\mak_redneck.json
msgid "It's not safe to go out at night. Not unless you're armed, that is!."
msgstr "晚上出門不安全。除非你帶著武器，那就另當別論！"

#: .\New NPCs\mak_redneck.json
msgid ""
"Food at our trailers is getting a little sparse, we'll need to start "
"scavenging soon."
msgstr "我們拖車裡的食物有點不夠了，得儘快開始搜尋物資。"

#: .\New NPCs\mak_redneck.json
msgid ""
"At least the government is off our backs now! Although I wouldn't mind a "
"little help considering how awful things are now."
msgstr "至少政府現在不管我們了！不過考慮到現在情況這麼糟糕，我倒不介意得到一點幫助。"

#: .\New NPCs\mak_redneck.json
msgid "What are you doin' about 'round these parts?"
msgstr "你在這附近做什麼？"

#: .\New NPCs\mak_redneck.json
msgid ""
"Why are you guys hanging around this trailer park, it seems a bit sparse."
msgstr "你們為什麼待在這個拖車公園，這裡看起來有點荒涼。"

#: .\New NPCs\mak_redneck.json
msgid ""
"Well, we decided not to leave when the government set up the New England "
"Exclusion zone. Who knows where they were taking all those people anyway, we"
" all know FEMA isn't worth a damn to anyone of us. They treat us like "
"garbage and mock our way of life, then expect us to leave and go to goodness"
" knows where at the drop of a hat, I don't think so! But yeah, things are a "
"bit rough now as you can see."
msgstr ""
"嗯，政府設立新英格蘭隔離區時，我們決定不離開。誰知道他們要把那些人帶到哪裡去，我們都知道聯邦應急管理局對我們這些人來說一文不值。他們把我們當垃圾，嘲笑我們的生活方式，然後指望我們立刻離開去天知道的地方，我才不幹呢！不過，你也看到了，現在情況確實有點艱難。"

#: .\New NPCs\mak_shelter_guard.json
msgid "Shelter Guard"
msgstr "避難所守衛"

#: .\New NPCs\mak_shelter_guard.json
msgid "A Guard of an LMOE shelter."
msgstr "一個LMOE避難所的守衛。"

#: .\New NPCs\mak_shelter_guard.json
msgid ""
"How did you even get in here? Was the door really just unlocked like that?."
msgstr "你到底是怎麼進來的？門真的就這麼沒鎖嗎？"

#: .\New NPCs\mak_shelter_guard.json
msgid "I have a gun and I'm willing to use it, don't tempt me!."
msgstr "我有槍，而且不介意使用它，別逼我！"

#: .\New NPCs\mak_shelter_guard.json
msgid "You think you can take me on, who do you think you are?"
msgstr "你以為你能對付我，你算老幾？"

#: .\New NPCs\mak_shelter_guard.json NPCs\mak_shelter_survivor.json
msgid "How did you even find our shelter?"
msgstr "你到底是怎麼找到我們的避難所的？"

#: .\New NPCs\mak_shelter_guard.json NPCs\mak_shelter_survivor.json
msgid ""
"What's it like for a woman out there in the exclusion zone? Is it dangerous?"
msgstr "在隔離區裡，一個女人過得怎麼樣？危險嗎？"

#: .\New NPCs\mak_shelter_guard.json NPCs\mak_shelter_survivor.json
msgid ""
"What's it like for a man out there in the exclusion zone? Have you found "
"anything interesting?"
msgstr "在隔離區裡，一個男人過得怎麼樣？有沒有發現什麼有趣的東西？"

#: .\New NPCs\mak_shelter_guard.json NPCs\mak_shelter_survivor.json
msgid "How long have you been hiding in this shelter?"
msgstr "你在這個避難所裡躲了多久了？"

#: .\New NPCs\mak_shelter_guard.json
msgid ""
"I don't really know, it's been too long. I've just been guarding these "
"people for any potential threats from the outside world, but nothing has "
"come here before you decided to traipse into our little domain."
msgstr "我也不太清楚，已經太久了。我一直在這裡守衛這些人，防備外界潛在的威脅，但在你決定闖入我們的小地盤之前，什麼都沒有來過。"

#: .\New NPCs\mak_shelter_survivor.json
msgid "Shelter Survivor"
msgstr "避難所幸存者"

#: .\New NPCs\mak_shelter_survivor.json
msgid "A citizen of New England who found their way to a LMOE shelter."
msgstr "一個找到LMOE避難所的新英格蘭居民。"

#: .\New NPCs\mak_shelter_survivor.json
msgid ""
"We have enough food in here to last for months, potentially even a year!."
msgstr "我們這裡的食物足夠維持幾個月，甚至可能一年！"

#: .\New NPCs\mak_shelter_survivor.json
msgid ""
"It's not safe for us to leave the shelter, maybe the guard can, but we "
"certainly can't."
msgstr "我們離開庇護所不安全，也許守衛可以，但我們肯定不行。"

#: .\New NPCs\mak_shelter_survivor.json
msgid ""
"I hope we don't run low on supplies, then we'll have to scavenge out there "
"in the exclusion zone."
msgstr "希望我們的補給不會耗盡，否則就得去隔離區那邊搜尋物資了。"

#: .\New NPCs\mak_shelter_survivor.json
msgid ""
"Goodness knows how long! At least a few weeks, maybe a few months? It is "
"truly hard to say. Me and a few others got in here when they were creating "
"the exclusion zone and haven't left since. The guard leaves sometimes, but "
"information about the surface is still rather sparse."
msgstr ""
"天知道要多久！至少幾周，也許幾個月？真的很難說。我和其他幾個人在設立隔離區時就進來了，之後再沒離開過。守衛有時會出去，但關於地表的信息仍然相當稀少。"

#: .\New NPCs\Militia NPCs\Talk_amg_leader.json
msgid ""
"Can't you see that I'm busy? whatever you wan't make sure it's important."
msgstr "沒看見我正忙著嗎？不管你想要什麼，確保它很重要。"

#: .\New NPCs\Militia NPCs\Talk_amg_leader.json
msgid "What's it like being a leader of a militia?"
msgstr "當民兵組織的領導者是什麼感覺？"

#: .\New NPCs\Militia NPCs\Talk_amg_leader.json
msgid "Do you have a task for me?"
msgstr "你有任務給我嗎？"

#: .\New NPCs\Militia NPCs\Talk_amg_leader.json
msgid ""
"To be honest with you, it's easier now then it was when the society was "
"still the way it was only a short while ago. The new denizens of New England"
" might be dangerous, but we can organize without the same fear of powerful "
"institutions bearing down on us at the slightest whiff of our presence."
msgstr ""
"老實說，現在比社會還像不久前的樣子時要容易些。新英格蘭的新居民可能很危險，但我們可以組織起來，而不用擔心強大的機構一察覺到我們的存在就對我們施壓。"

#: .\New NPCs\Militia NPCs\amg_gkb_guardnpc.json
msgid "What are you doing around here, what do you want from me?"
msgstr "你在這附近做什麼，想從我這裡得到什麼？"

#: .\New NPCs\Militia NPCs\amg_gkb_guardnpc.json
msgid "So you're a member of a miltia, what's this place about anyway?"
msgstr "所以你是民兵組織的一員，這地方到底是幹什麼的？"

#: .\New NPCs\Militia NPCs\amg_gkb_guardnpc.json
msgid ""
"I'm glad to see somebody taken's a bit of genuine interest in us, that "
"usually didn't mean well before the Cataclysm but now we can take any chance"
" we get. We fortified this little compound when the exclusion zone was set "
"up, now this is where most of us stay."
msgstr ""
"很高興看到有人對我們表現出真正的興趣，這在大災變前通常不懷好意，但現在我們可以抓住任何機會。我們在隔離區設立時加固了這個小營地，現在這裡是我們大多數人的居所。"

#: .\New NPCs\Militia NPCs\amg_guard.json
msgid "Militia Member"
msgstr "民兵成員"

#: .\New NPCs\Militia NPCs\amg_guard.json
msgid "Is a member of a militia group."
msgstr "是民兵組織的成員。"

#: .\New NPCs\Militia NPCs\amg_gun_merchant.json
msgid "Militia Merchant"
msgstr "民兵商人"

#: .\New NPCs\Militia NPCs\amg_gun_merchant.json
msgid "I'm a local shopkeeper."
msgstr "我是本地店主。"

#: .\New NPCs\Militia NPCs\amg_gun_merchant.json
msgid "What are you buying, what are you selling?"
msgstr "你想買什麼，賣什麼？"

#: .\New NPCs\Militia NPCs\amg_gun_merchant.json
msgid "What is it like being a merchant around here?"
msgstr "在這附近當商人是什麼感覺？"

#: .\New NPCs\Militia NPCs\amg_gun_merchant.json
msgid "See you later."
msgstr "回頭見。"

#: .\New NPCs\Militia NPCs\amg_gun_merchant.json
msgid ""
"Living in the compound has its own difficulties, for sure. At least now we "
"don't have to worry about losing our jobs or getting thrown in jail for uh "
"competition reasons essentially"
msgstr "住在營地裡肯定有它的難處。至少現在我們不用擔心因為呃競爭原因而失業或被關進監獄。"

#: .\New NPCs\Militia NPCs\amg_gun_merchant.json
msgid "Got it."
msgstr "明白了。"

#: .\New NPCs\Militia NPCs\amg_leader.json
msgid "Militia Local Leader"
msgstr "民兵地方領袖"

#: .\New NPCs\Militia NPCs\amg_leader.json
msgid "A local leader of a miltia."
msgstr "民兵組織的地方領袖。"
